# Project guide reference

Before implementing or refactoring major features in `sokany-storefront`, read:

`.cursor/PROJECT_GUIDE.md`

Use it to find:

- Customer, admin, and driver routes
- API endpoints and core `src/lib/` files
- WordPress plugin locations (OTP, headless settings)
- Changelog of prior session work
- Environment variables and deployment defaults

When adding a significant feature, append a short entry to the changelog section in `PROJECT_GUIDE.md`.
